snippet.title: 'Morphed' video controversy: Sheetal Mhatre lashes out at Uddhav faction
snippet.description:
Former corporator from Dahisar Sheetal Mhatre lashed out at Uddhav Thackeray faction after an objectionable video, allegedly morphed, showing Shiv Sena MLA Prakash Surve with her went viral on social media. The video zooms in on Surve and Mhatre as the two join CM Eknath Shinde's cavalcade. Mhatre marched to Dahisar police station in the wee hours of Sunday to lodge a complaint against the miscreants. The police have arrested two persons in connection with the case. Mhatre released a video and said," When your opponents have nothing left to target you with, they stoop to such cheap tactics. Targeting a woman who is someone's mother, daughter, wife with a video like this is disturbing. Everyone knows who is behind this. It's shocking that something like this can be peddled to malign, defame us. Those who are behind this have no ground to stand on and that's why they are stopping to this level."

#uddhavthackeray #mumbai #latestnews

snippet.description:
‡∞®‡∞æ‡∞ü‡±Å, ‡∞®‡∞æ‡∞ü‡±Å‡∞®‡±Å ‡∞Ü‡∞∏‡±ç‡∞ï‡∞æ‡∞∞‡±ç ‡∞Ö‡∞µ‡∞æ‡∞∞‡±ç‡∞°‡±Å ‡∞é‡∞Ç‡∞¶‡±Å‡∞ï‡±Å ‡∞µ‡∞∞‡∞ø‡∞Ç‡∞ö‡∞ø‡∞Ç‡∞¶‡∞ø? || Why Natu Natu won Oscar award? ||
Oscars 2023: RRR's Naatu Naatu wins best original song
The song Naatu Naatu from the hit Telugu-language film RRR has made history by becoming the first Indian film song to win an Oscar.

The blockbuster track won Best Original Song at the 95th Academy Awards, beating heavyweights like Lady Gaga and Rihanna.

Its catchy tempo and choreography has captivated audiences around the world.

India won a second Oscar for The Elephant Whisperers which won in the Best Documentary Short film category.

The documentary, which tells the story of a couple who care for an injured baby elephant after it gets separated from its herd, is the first Indian production to win in this category.
https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-india-64935389

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3717 - 13 Mar 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3717: Aage Ki Soch
--------------------------------------------------------
Tapu's friend keeps calling Jetha to speak to Tapu regarding some matter, which obviously makes Jetha irritated. Jetha tells Tapu not to give his phone number to his friends. Later, Iyer and Babita visit the Gadas. Iyer's TV remote has stopped functioning, and he needs it fixed by evening. Jetha checks the remote, but Tapu intervenes to help. Instead of helping, Tapu accidentally drops the remote. Now, Iyer gets really worried because in the evening people are coming over to his place to watch a speech by an eminent scientist. Will Jetha be able to fix Iyer's TV remote on time?

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3717, 13 Mar 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Farq Episode 39 - [Eng Sub] - Faysal Quraishi - Sehar Khan - Adeel Chaudhry - 13th March 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Farq is the story of two different individuals, Irsa (Sehar Khan) and Kamal (Faysal Quraishi) who come together to form an unusual union under compromising circumstances. 
From the outside, Irsa and Kamal seem not to be made for each other. They are too different in terms of character, life choices, desires and socio-economic background. 
On one hand, Irsa desires to live a life of luxury while Kamal is fed up with the loneliness that his house offers. Despite being together as a couple, 
will the two ever look at the truth in themselves to determine who they are and what they want in life?

Written By: Imran Nazir
Directed By: Aehsun Talish
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

snippet.title: The Little Mermaid | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch and you'll see, some day I'll be, part of your world! Watch the new trailer for #TheLittleMermaid and see the movie in theaters May 26!

The brand new soundtrack for Disney‚Äôs ‚ÄúThe Little Mermaid‚Äù is available now to Pre-Save, Pre-Add or Pre-Order ‚Äì¬†https://presave.umusic.com/thelittlemermaidsoundtrack

‚ÄúThe Little Mermaid‚Äù is the beloved story of Ariel,¬†a beautiful and spirited young mermaid with a thirst for adventure. The youngest of King Triton‚Äôs daughters and the most defiant, Ariel longs to find out more about the world beyond the sea and, while visiting the surface, falls for the dashing Prince Eric.¬†While mermaids are forbidden to interact with humans, Ariel must follow her heart. She makes a deal with the evil sea witch, Ursula, which gives her a chance to experience life on land but ultimately places her life ‚Äì and her father‚Äôs crown ‚Äì in jeopardy. The film stars singer and¬†actress Halle Bailey (‚Äúgrown-ish‚Äù) as Ariel; Jonah Hauer-King (‚ÄúA Dog‚Äôs Way Home‚Äù) as Prince Eric; Tony Award¬Æ winner Daveed Diggs (‚ÄúHamilton‚Äù) as the voice of Sebastian; Awkwafina (‚ÄúRaya and the Last Dragon‚Äù) as the voice of Scuttle; Jacob Tremblay (‚ÄúLuca‚Äù) as the voice of Flounder; Noma Dumezweni (‚ÄúMary Poppins Returns‚Äù) as Queen Selina; Art Malik (‚ÄúHomeland‚Äù) as Sir Grimsby; with Oscar¬Æ winner Javier Bardem (‚ÄúNo Country for Old Men‚Äù) as King Triton; and two-time Academy Award¬Æ nominee Melissa McCarthy (‚ÄúCan You Ever Forgive Me?‚Äù ‚ÄúBridesmaids‚Äù) as Ursula. ¬†¬†¬†¬†¬†
¬†
‚ÄúThe Little Mermaid‚Äù is directed by Oscar¬Æ nominee Rob Marshall (‚ÄúChicago,‚Äù ‚ÄúMary Poppins Returns‚Äù) with a screenplay by two-time Oscar nominee David Magee (‚ÄúLife of Pi,‚Äù ‚ÄúFinding Neverland‚Äù). The songs feature music from multiple Academy Award¬Æ winner Alan Menken (‚ÄúBeauty and the Beast,‚Äù ‚ÄúAladdin‚Äù) and lyrics by Howard Ashman, and new lyrics by three-time Tony Award¬Æ winner Lin-Manuel Miranda. The film is produced by two-time Emmy¬Æ winner Marc Platt (‚ÄúJesus Christ Superstar Live in Concert,‚Äù ‚ÄúGrease Live!‚Äù), Miranda, two-time Emmy winner John DeLuca (‚ÄúTony Bennett: An American Classic‚Äù), and Rob Marshall, with Jeffrey Silver (‚ÄúThe Lion King‚Äù) serving as executive producer.¬†

Hashtag: #TheLittleMermaid

Facebook:¬†https://www.facebook.com/DisneyTheLittleMermaid
Instagram:¬†https://www.instagram.com/disneylittlemermaid/

*****Dr. Danish Salim*****

Dr Danish Salim; currently working as Specialist Emergency Department, Sheikh Khalifa Medical City, Abu Dubai, UAE Health Authority & Managing Director at Dr D Better Life Pvt Ltd. He was the academic director and head of the emergency department at PRS Hospital, Kerala. He has over 10 years of experience in emergency and critical care. He was awarded the SEHA Hero award and is one of the first doctors to receive a Golden Visa from the UAE Government for his contributions to Health Care.

He was active in the field of emergency medicine and have
contributed in bringing in multiple innovations for which Dr
Danish was awarded nationally as "Best innovator in emergency medicine and young achiever" as well as the ‚ÄúBest emergency physician of state award".

Among multiple innovations like app for accident alerts, jump kits for common emergency management, Dr Danish brought into being the state's first bike ambulance with KED and a single state wide-app to control and coordinate private and public ambulances under one platform with the help of Indian Medical Association and Kerala Police. This network was appreciated and is successfully running with the support of the government of Kerala currently.

Besides the technology field, Dr Danish was enthusiastic in conducting more than 2000 structured emergency training classes for common men, residents, doctors and healthcare professionals over the span of 5 years.

Positions Held

1. Kerala state Secretary: Society for Emergency Medicine India

2. National Innovation Head Society for Emergency Medicine India

3. Vice President Indian Medical Association Kovalam

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance, as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Nikah Episode 53 - [Eng Sub] - Haroon Shahid - Zainab Shabbir - 13th March 2023  - HAR PAL GEO

Nikah is a powerful and inspiring story of a young girl‚Äôs fight for her social and religious rights. 
Opinionated and confident by nature, Anusha is a beautiful young girl who knows how to stand up for her rights. After losing her mother at a young age, Anusha has been brought up by her aunt, Umaima with a lot of love and care. Umamia is a bit hesitant about Anusha‚Äôs assertiveness and often makes her understand.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3716 - 11 Mar 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3716: Khujli Powder Ka Sach
--------------------------------------------------------
Dr. Hathi comes to Bhide's rescue as he has been continuously itching. Dr. Hathi asks Tapu Sena to put water on Bhide and asks Abdul to get some fresh soil from the garden. Everyone is shocked to see the new style of treating a patient with itchiness. Later Dr. Hathi asks Bhide to apply the soil on his body and asks him to go for a bath. Bhide comes back and to everyone's surprise, he has got rid of the itching. Dr. Hathi announces that this was not due to the gulal powder, Bhide realizes that he had applied some oil on his body before coming for the Holi festival. Madhavi is shocked as the oil had expired and she had thrown the oil bottle. Stay tuned.

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3716, 11 Mar 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Tere Bin Episode 21 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa BB Cream - 8th March 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally presented by Nisa BB Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq

Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises

snippet.title: "‡§Æ‡•à‡§Ç ‡§Æ‡§∞ ‡§≠‡•Ä ‡§ú‡§æ‡§§‡•Ä ‡§§‡•ã ‡§Æ‡§æ‡§Ç-‡§¨‡§æ‡§™ ‡§ï‡•ã ‡§ï‡•ã‡§à ‡§ó‡§Æ ‡§®‡§π‡•Ä‡§Ç ‡§π‡•ã‡§§‡§æ" | Savita Pradhan | Josh Talks Hindi
snippet.description:
Savita ‡§ú‡•Ä ‡§ï‡•Ä ‡§§‡§∞‡§π ‡§ï‡•ú‡•Ä ‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§®‡§§ ‡§î‡§∞ ‡•õ‡§ø‡§¶ ‡§∏‡•á ‡§ï‡§∞‡•á‡§Ç ‡§Ö‡§™‡§®‡§æ ‡§π‡§∞ ‡§∏‡§™‡§®‡§æ ‡§™‡•Ç‡§∞‡§æ: https://joshskills.app.link/ZxGvfIxQWxb

Savita ji was born in a tribal family in a small village "Mandi" of Madhya Pradesh, she was brought up in a very poor family. Savita ji used to walk with a limp in her childhood. But his courage never stopped walking. I was the first girl in this village who passed 12th. But life's difficulties had just begun. After marriage, they were tortured a lot, killed, beaten, and kept hungry. It had come to the point that he had even thought of hanging himself.
